        <main class="w-full bg-[#FBF5F0] max-w-[1920px] px-[20px] md:px-[10px] lg:px-[190px] xl:px-[150px] m-auto">

            <div class="w-full flex justify-center items-center py-[70px]">

                <div
                    class="max-w-[1142px] w-full bg-white px-[10px] py-[10px] shadow-lg flex flex-col gap-[20px] text-justify">

                    <h1 class="text-[merriweather] text-[28px] text-[#000000]">Shipping Policy</h1>

                    <dl class="space-y-8">
                        <!-- Shipping Policy Overview -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                1. Shipping Policy Overview
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Geldix Pharmaceuticals Private Limited is committed to delivering your orders in a
                                timely and
                                efficient manner. Our shipping policy outlines the terms and conditions related to the
                                delivery
                                of products purchased from our website.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Shipping Charges -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                2. Shipping Charges
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Shipping charges are calculated based on the total weight of your order, the delivery
                                location,
                                and the shipping method chosen at checkout. Any applicable shipping charges will be
                                displayed at
                                checkout before you complete your purchase.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Delivery Timeframes -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                3. Delivery Timeframes
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Orders are typically processed within 1-2 business days. Delivery times may vary
                                depending on
                                your location, but we aim to deliver orders within 5-7 business days. Please note that
                                these
                                timeframes are estimates and may be affected by factors beyond our control.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Order Tracking -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                4. Order Tracking
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Once your order has been shipped, you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking
                                number.
                                You can use this tracking number to monitor the status of your delivery on the courier's
                                website.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Shipping Restrictions -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                5. Shipping Restrictions
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Currently, we only ship to addresses within India. We do not deliver to P.O. boxes,
                                APO/FPO
                                addresses, or international locations. Please ensure that the shipping address provided
                                is
                                accurate and complete to avoid delays.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Damaged or Lost Items -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                6. Damaged or Lost Items
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                If your order arrives damaged or is lost in transit, please contact us immediately at
                                <a href="mailto:info@geldix.in?subject=Damaged product whill shipping&body=Hello Geldix Pharmaceuticals" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600" >info@geldix.in</a> with your order details. We will work with the shipping carrier to
                                resolve the issue and provide a replacement or refund as necessary.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                7. Changes to This Policy
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Geldix Pharmaceuticals Private Limited reserves the right to modify this shipping policy
                                at any
                                time. Any changes will be posted on this page and will take effect immediately. Please
                                review
                                this policy periodically to stay informed about our shipping practices.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Contact Information -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                8. Contact Information
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                If you have any questions or concerns about this Shipping Policy, please contact us at
                                <a href="mailto:info@geldix.in?subject=Question about shipping policy&body=Hello Geldix Pharmaceuticals" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600" >info@geldix.in</a> or visit our office at <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/7iSA9uBCFWpqXsrh8" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600"> Shop 2, Katara Hills, Rapadia Village, 462043, Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India </a>.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                    </dl>


